# Codebase Structure

## Overview

CreatorOSX architecture is evolving from a simple landing page to a full-stack SaaS application:

- **Current:** Flat Vite structure (landing page)
- **Target:** Next.js 14 App Router structure (MVP)

This document covers both architectures and the migration strategy.

