## Directory Roles

### Root Level (`/`)

**Purpose:** Core entry files and configuration

**Contains:**

- `App.tsx` - Main component that imports and arranges all sections
- `index.tsx` - React bootstrapping with StrictMode
- `index.html` - HTML shell, Tailwind config, font loading
- Configuration files (tsconfig, vite.config, package.json)
- Documentation (README.md)

**Philosophy:** Keep the root minimal and organized. Only entry points and config files belong here.

---

### `/components/`

**Purpose:** All page sections and layout components

**Organization:**

- One component per file
- Named after their purpose/section
- Self-contained with inline styles (Tailwind)
- Can contain co-located sub-components

