## Import Patterns

### Standard Import Order

```typescript
// 1. React core
import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react";

// 2. Third-party libraries
import { Icon1, Icon2 } from "lucide-react";
import { AreaChart, Area } from "recharts";

// 3. Local components
import { Button } from "./ui/Button";
import { Header } from "./components/Header";

// 4. Types (if in separate files)
import type { MyType } from "./types";
```

### Path Alias Usage

The project supports `@/` alias pointing to root:

```typescript
// ✅ Can use (configured in vite.config.ts)
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/Button";

// ✅ Also valid (relative path)
import { Button } from "./ui/Button";

// Choose one style and be consistent
```

**Current pattern:** Relative paths are used throughout (no `@/` usage yet)

